abstract="In order to prevent the spread of COVID-19, online education has become a learning way for primary and secondary schools and universities. However, the rapid development of online education faces many challenges. In recent years, Artificial Intelligence (AI) technology has been developed rapidly and applied in different industries. Therefore, many problems in online education can also be improved through AI technology, so as to improve the quality of online education, and make education improve. This paper mainly analyzes the integration of AI technology and online education to solve the problems faced by students in online learning. At the same time of reducing the burden of education participants, let AI technology play a better role, and help education develop from traditional offline mode to online and offline complementary direction.",
