abstract="We describe the development and use of a new conceptual design system, called SandBOX, which combines a range of intuitive interfaces with real-time analysis, thus enabling a wide variety of users to develop performative concept designs. We show how this interactive design platform can overcome some of the limitations of current physical model-based design processes, whilst retaining many of their advantages.",
