abstract="According to analysis of the problem of parking difficulty in city and insufficient functions of navigation APPs at present, try to design a new city intelligent parking service system from the perspective of professional interactive design, practically provide comprehensive and comfortable parking and travel experiences to users. With the operational procedure and functions of navigation APP and parking APP as the research object, analyze the problems existing in the service system of parking navigation APP. Investigate the personal experience of user using current parking navigation APP, and improve the service system of parking navigation APP from the seven aspects of time, space, user, usage behavior, information, scenario and technology. By utilizing real-time positioning, real-time update of data and dynamic vehicle search technology, provide suggestion and guidance for user to park their car, and improve the parking and travel efficiency. In order to improve the city parking efficiency and strengthen the travel comfort of people, current parking resources must be fully utilized. The parking data should be integrated and effectively used, in-depth analysis of the interactive design components should be conducted, and the efficient and convenient intelligent parking service system can only be designed from the perspective of user's requirements.",
