abstract="With the increasing demand of the internet in the 21st century, we have the challenges to secure our network and data so, for we demand some software and devices to protect our system. However, these devices want high computational power and have a complex structure. We use firewall and IDS/IPS as an intermediary device and software for protecting our systems. An Intrusion Detection System used to monitor network traffic, and if any suspicious activity is occurring, it will automatically notify the security person to secure future access.",
