title="Out of the Box, into the Cubes: Envisioning User Experiences Through a Tool for Gamification, Toyification and Playification",
booktitle="Interactivity, Game Creation, Design, Learning, and Innovation",
year="2020",
publisher="Springer International Publishing",
address="Cham",
