abstract="In academic institutions the lab sessions for students are usually limited to 1--2 slots per week and at specified time only. This duration of time will not be enough if one wants to try anything beyond listed experiments. The need of the hour here is round-the-clock lab access to students. The primary goal is to empower academic institutions and industries to utilize their resources (hardware and software tools), round-the-clock to enable their users to access their resources from the comfort of their homes.",
